<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-521] config mistake in Persistent Client Cache </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-521</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In sector&#160; 27.3.1.&#160;Add a PCC backend on a client, there is an example:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
client&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;# lctl pcc add /mnt/lustre /mnt/pcc  --param &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote-red&quot;&gt;&quot;projid={500,1000}&amp;amp;fname={*.h5},uid=1001 rwid=2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-bash&quot;&gt;
client&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;# lctl pcc add /mnt/lustre /mnt/pcc  --param &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote-red&quot;&gt;&quot;projid={500,1000}&amp;amp;fname={*.h5},uid={1001} rwid=2&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
